cset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Alec-baldwin-header.jpg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Alec-baldwin-header-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Alec-baldwin-header-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Alec-baldwin-header-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Alec-baldwin-header-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Alec-baldwin-header-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alec-baldwin">Alec Baldwin</a> has opened up about how he is coping after the fatal shooting that occurred on the set of his Western movie <i>Rust</i> in 2021.</p><p> <b>READ MORE:</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rust-director-says-he-says-no-relationship-with-alec-baldwin-3784466"><b>&#39;Rust&#39; director says he has “no relationship” with Alec Baldwin following fatal shooting</b></a></p><p> As reported by <a href="https://people.com/alec-baldwin-asks-why-couldnt-it-have-been-me-after-fatal-rust-shooting-11683821" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>People</i></a> , in the first episode of his new reality show <i>The Baldwins</i> , the actor and his wife Hilaria share some insight into what they&#39;ve been going through since the shooting and following trial.</p><p> During the episode, Baldwin said: “This has been just surreal. I mean, I can&#39;t even believe that we&#39;re going through this, and I always feel more in pain about you than me, because I think to myself, well, you know, I&#39;m going to try to my best to just get through it, and I think what it&#39;s done to you and how much it&#39;s hurt you and everything.” </p><figure id="attachment_3840205" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840205" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840205" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-con