t-evidence-3774605">case against the actor was dismissed last July</a> , and officially <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/alec-baldwin-rust-set-shooting-case-concludes-after-prosecutors-drop-appeal-3824716">concluded in December 2024</a> after New Mexico prosecutors decided not to pursue an appeal of the court&#39;s decision to dismiss an involuntary manslaughter charge against him. Baldwin has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/alec-baldwin-sues-for-malicious-prosecution-following-rust-manslaughter-trial-3828107">since filed a lawsuit</a> against the district attorney and other Santa Fe officials for malicious prosecution and civil rights violations.</p><p> <i>The Baldwins</i> is a new TLC show that sees Baldwin and Hilaria invite cameras into their home to document life with their seven children. </p><figure id="attachment_3774606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774606" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774606" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/AlecBaldwin-RustTrial-Getty.jpg" alt="" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/AlecBaldwin-RustTrial-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/AlecBaldwin-RustTrial-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/AlecBaldwin-RustTrial-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/AlecBaldwin-RustTrial-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/AlecBaldwin-RustTrial-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774606" class="wp-caption-text"> Alec Baldwin with his attorney Alex Spiro upon the announcement of the judge&#39;s ruling. CREDIT: Ramsay de Give-Pool/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> In it, Hilaria opened up about Alec&#39;s emotional state since the <i>Rust</i> incident. She said: “Everyone who is close to Alec has seen his mental health decline. He was diagnosed with PTSD, and he says in his darkest moments, &#39;If an accident had to have happened this day, why am I still here? Why couldn&#39;t it have been me?&#39;”</p><p> She continued: “You wake up in the morning and you&#39;re like, &#39;Oh god, why did I wake up?&#39;”</p><p> Baldwin, referring to his response when a friend asked how he was doing, said: “I said, &#39;I&#39;m happier when I&#39;m asleep than when I&#39;m awake&#39;.”</p><p> The actor has spoken out about how the shooting has impacted him previously, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/alec-baldwin-doesnt-want-to-see-rust-this-is-obviously-the-most-difficult-thing-ive-ever-dealt-with-3815866">saying in November 2024 that he never wants to see <i>Rust</i></a> . He also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/alec-baldwin-vows-to-expose-the-truth-of-rust-shooting-theres-more-to-come-3823684">said that “there is more to come”</a> regarding the incident when appearing on a podcast last December, and that “the truth of what happened has never been told”.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/alec-baldwin-mental-health-rust-shooting-3840204">Alec Baldwin reflects on “terrible” mental health decline post-&#39;Rust&#39; shooting: “I&#39;m happier when I&#39;m asleep”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
